flowRoot.flowPara: Thousands of diverse contributors make GNOME a reality. Anyone can contribute and there are a lot of different things to do. You can use and improve your skills in coding, design or writing, and will meet many friends of all ages and walks of life in the process.

We are happy to provide full guidance to anyone who wants to become a part of the GNOME community. Our GNOME Love initiative provides a series of easy-to-follow resources, and introduces you to over 40 mentors available to help you get started at any time.
Join us. Get involved! What do you want to do?
